  "description": "Boutique Chain showcase: Cathedral as primary character effect. ORACLE at moderate stochasticity produces tonal events. Cathedral at PacketLoss 0.35 (significant digital degradation) and BitCrush 0.30 transforms the GENDY tones into artifacts of themselves — prophecies encoded in lossy format, part of the information missing. SunMix 0.4 vs DarkMix 0.6 maintains a tension between spectral brightness and darkness. ModDepth 0.5 adds modulation to the Cathedral's reverb character over time. Anomaly minimal. Archive Chance 0.06 (rare memory retrievals). Submersion 3 stages. The effect is ORACLE at its most oracular: degraded, prophetic, not fully intelligible.",
